{"tid":2408464,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"車公廟善信排隊登記拒掃碼","createTime":"2021-02-15T03:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T07:25:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c96e780d79bcfb5b09e93b1ec44d91ca9eb2c5d1","tid":2408464,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210215/JILPHPPCDRGMZPLZQFZRXFAZ6Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210215%2FJILPHPPCDRGMZPLZQFZRXFAZ6Y%2F&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eQX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=3c54be20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210215%2FJILPHPPCDRGMZPLZQFZRXFAZ6Y%2F&h=acb1a78d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210215/JILPHPPCDRGMZPLZQFZRXFAZ6Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n車公廟善信排隊登記拒掃碼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】大年初三赤口，市民不宜拜年，轉而湧往拜車公。車公廟今年新規定，入廟者須使用安心出行流動應用程式或由職員登記個人資料，雖然以手機掃描二維碼比起登記個人資料快，不過大多數善信仍然選擇後者。有善信坦言擔心私隱外洩，日後亦不會安裝安心出行應用程式。昨日共有17,473人次進入車公廟，比起去年同日的約4.7萬人次大跌逾六成。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：四廈赤口強檢 居民轟阻拜神<br />\n<br />\n車公廟前晚11時重開，通宵。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OVT2-wtz4qsvU4BrZgevdy5YZiM=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SUGO6XJBMFFR5MRHRWWKCFVJEE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOVT2-wtz4qsvU4BrZgevdy5YZiM%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSUGO6XJBMFFR5MRHRWWKCFVJEE.jpg&h=084431e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■車公廟外大批善信排隊等候職員以人手登記資料，「安心出行」通道卻無人問津。<br />\n<br />\n早上11時半到場的劉先生，排隊至下午1時許。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：安心碼加藍牙技術 月底實測自動嘟  專家：可提升至全球定位<br />\n<br />\n十多年來均會到車公廟拜神的李小姐。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/z-mShNInJ7xAtIDB9uV9ehpU-kw=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JZFKQWNFHZGXTFCZTG73GN2PTU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fz-mShNInJ7xAtIDB9uV9ehpU-kw%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJZFKQWNFHZGXTFCZTG73GN2PTU.jpg&h=c78eb7d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■車公廟職員用紙筆記錄善信個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「安心」通道無人龍<br />\n<br />\n她與家人均選擇以人手登記資料入廟，提到為何不使用安心出行應用程式，「其實我哋都唔裝㗎喇，啲私隱呀各樣嘢，都會擔心呢啲」。被問到是否不相信政府，她笑言「唔講咁多呢啲啦！」。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n由於輪候人數眾多，華人廟宇委。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n華人廟宇委員會秘書處表示，昨日上午8時至下午5時30分，車公廟共有17,473人次進廟。車公廟今晨7時起重開，至下午5時30分關閉。此開放時間將會沿用至正月十九、即下月2日。"},{"pid":"ae4c70821e9002f11c9723fc20c24a8ae2f5f858","tid":2408464,"uid":18012,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"製造就業<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大量登記員"},{"pid":"98861ee360a651f1b0b18dce82d8a628714204f4","tid":2408464,"uid":2924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T03:43:52.000Z","msg":"宗仔個玻璃心碎左未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b54f86510a648e70e85cda8ac069ed91616194d","tid":2408464,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae4c70821e9002f11c9723fc20c24a8ae2f5f858","tid":2408464,"uid":18012,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"製造就業<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大量登記員"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T03:52:41.000Z","msg":"安心登記員"},{"pid":"600a1d2138649d40480787680d57aec776d46a4b","tid":2408464,"uid":237425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T04:08:21.000Z","msg":"登記淨口講都得？應該無權睇身分證呀?"},{"